The paper discusses the development of a new database system that can manage multiple data models, which is a core topic in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the need for flexible schema and unified query processing, which are topics related to data structures (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper proposes a unified database management system, which involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) and software engineering principles (cs.SE).
